value.name: Portland Police Identify Man Shot By Officer As Terrell Kyreem Johnson

value.name: terrell johnson
value.description: The Multnomah County Grand Jury found Portland Police Officer Samson Ajir to be justified in the May 10 shooting that killed Terrell Kyreem Johnson.
